d are associated with Web 2.0. Created in 2001, Wikipedia has become the world&amp;rsquo;s most visited wiki.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Nginx: Installation and Configuration as an Apache Alternative</title><link>https://wiki.deimos.fr/Nginx_:_Installation_et_configuration_d'une_alternative_d'Apache/</link><pubDate>Fri, 29 Aug 2014 15:33:00 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://wiki.deimos.fr/Nginx_:_Installation_et_configuration_d'une_alternative_d'Apache/</guid><description>&lt;p>










